{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763040221,"sessionID":"ses_126a6a1e9ffedEMNRMHv06v6Ez","part":{"id":"prt_ed95a4ade001vZj8Z3nPsSi8Hh","messageID":"msg_ed95a18fe001rHpM3r0FG5EE16","sessionID":"ses_126a6a1e9ffedEMNRMHv06v6Ez","type":"text","text":"The loop contract conflicts with a fully manual hand-roll in normal use, but this is already a command-owned fan-out lineage handoff with an explicit artifact root override. I’ll mirror the required phase outputs directly in that lineage packet and use the reducer/state schema rather than spawning nested agents.","time":{"start":1781763033822,"end":1781763040219},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c5728e2594de0e4016a338bd9c8f8819190faee23049b5d04","phase":"commentary"}}}}
